|GKO================================================================
                   |WKOGarou Guild : General Commands
|GKO================================================================
|YKOIn addition to the combat abilities and spiritual powers
listed in |RKO'ghelp shaman'|YKO, |RKO'ghelp guardian'|YKO, and |RKO'ghelp warrior'|YKO,
all Garou have access to the following commands regardless of
dedication.

|WKO[Usable in all forms]
|CKOgsc         |WKO- Display your stats and other information
|CKObalance     |WKO- Display your spiritual state
|CKOws          |WKO- Communicate with other Garou
|CKOgaea        |WKO- Communicate with both Garou and Druids
|CKOpt          |WKO- Communicate with your fellow pack members
|CKOtransform   |WKO- Shift between physical forms
|CKOconsider    |WKO- Size up an opponent
|CKOwsmell      |WKO- Sniff around for nearby opponents
|CKOsense       |WKO- Sense who or what a person or wolf really is
|CKOscent       |WKO- Find a particular foe, or path to guildhall
|CKOremember    |WKO- Display the locations of your buried items
|CKOforget      |WKO- Forget about your buried items
|CKOwolflong    |WKO- Set your wolf long description
|CKOcrinoslong  |WKO- Set your crinos long description
|CKOgupdatehist |WKO- Display a list recent guild updates
|CKOhowl        |WKO- Communicate with a great howl
|CKOdig         |WKO- Dig up loot you have already buried


|WKO[Usable in wolf/crinos]
|CKOchase       |WKO- Toggle off/on chasing of foes
|CKOeat         |WKO- Eat a corpse to restore health
|CKObury        |WKO- Bury an item in the ground

|WKO[Usable only in wolf]
|CKOcarry       |WKO- Pickup an item in your mouth
|CKOspit        |WKO- Spit out an item that you are carrying
|CKOblend       |WKO- Blend into the scenery hiding from foes
|CKOemergency   |WKO- Send out an emergency message to all Immortals
